the B-SPLINE quadrangle is defined by INTERPOLATION POINTS.
Give the NAME or click each INTERPOLATION POINT in the order

For j=1 until  number of points in the Y direction
    For i=1 until  number of points in the X direction
        Give the POINT(i,j) NAME

Example: 5; 2;  P11;P21;P31;P41;P51;  P12;P22;P32;P42;P52;
 
           for a location of points
            P12  P22  P32  P42  P52

            P11  P21  P31  P41  P51

In fact, the view angle is chosen as you want
but after, the order is defined above.
